headline: This 4%-Yielding Dividend Stock Adds Another $1.3 Billion of Fuel to Its Growth Engine
summary: Kidner Morgan added another $1.3 billion of expansion projects in the second quarter.  Strong growth catalysts position it to continue approving new expansion projects.  Kinder Morgan (NYSE: KMI) has experienced a resurgence in growth over the past year.
